CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 8, 1941, pg. 9, reads: "Nurses To Have Dance Wednesday - The local association of registered nurses will have their first dance of the season March 12th at the Cottage Inn, featuring the Sunset Royals. Left to right: Mrs. Pauline H. Horde, Mrs. Christine Williams, Miss Ruth Comer, Mrs. Florence T. Lanier, Miss Ruby Hatcher. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five women, front row from left: Pauline H. Horde, Ruth Comer, Ruby Hatcher; back row: Christine Williams, and Florence T. Lanier, posed in front of light colored circular background in Harris Studio
